304
00:20:27,920 --> 00:20:30,080
What's in there?


305
00:20:53,290 --> 00:20:54,370
Monster!


306
00:20:54,540 --> 00:20:55,350
What's that?


307
00:20:55,590 --> 00:20:58,180
Gargoyle? That's the first time I see one.


308
00:20:58,290 --> 00:20:59,360
Gargoyle?


309
00:20:59,970 --> 00:21:01,300
It's a man-made creature.


310
00:21:02,210 --> 00:21:03,880
Is it dead?


311
00:21:04,200 --> 00:21:06,600
They said that if you drain its body fluid
to mummify it,


312
00:21:06,740 --> 00:21:09,830
